B2B SAAS GROWTH FRAMEWORK — Meridian Digital Ltd

A 28-page framework for UK B2B SaaS companies at the £1–10M ARR stage. The framework integrates the three channels that actually move the needle for scaling SaaS businesses — SEO, paid (Google + LinkedIn), and product-led motions — into a single operating model tied to CAC, LTV and payback targets by ARR stage. It opens with a stage-based diagnostic: where your company sits today, what the next inflection point looks like, and which channels typically deliver the highest marginal return at each stage.

The SEO chapter details our content cluster strategy for SaaS — mapping commercial-intent keywords to product surfaces, building bottom-of-funnel landing pages that actually convert, and engineering content for AI Overview citation so that the ongoing shift from clicks to citations works in your favour. The paid chapters walk through the LinkedIn Ads playbook (audience layering, creative principles, retargeting cadence) and the Google Ads playbook (branded, competitor, category, long-tail) including the budget allocation logic we use across stages.

The framework closes with product-led growth motion design, a sales-assisted PLG hybrid model for enterprise deals, an attribution and dashboarding section that ties every touchpoint back to pipeline, and a 12-month growth roadmap template. Designed for founders, heads of growth and CMOs who need an opinionated, executable plan rather than a menu of options.
